                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17170227-36-off176 t17170227-36-cd177"></join>. The Prosecutor deposed, that the Wig hung upon a high Block in the Window, and that he hearing a Noise in the Night, came down, but saw no body, but next Morning found the Glass of the Sash broke, that was against the Light hole of the Shutter, and the Wig gone. 
